gomodel:SYNGO_2213  a     owl:Ontology ;
        rdfs:comment      "Rationale: LRFN1 was enriched in postsynaptic density fractions.\n\n15/01/2018 Pim\n- Fig.3: \"SALM2 Colocalizes and Associates with PSD-95 at Excitatory Synapses\"\n- Based on the known transmembrane topology of the protein, the \"integral component of ... membrane\" term was chosen.. Experimental description: Experimental Procedures\nBrain Fractionation and Coimmunoprecipitation\nSubcellular and PSD fractions of adult rat brain were prepared.\n\n15/01/2018 Pim\n- Overexpressed SALM2 is of rat species: \". Full-length rat SALM2 (aa 1-766) was PCR-amplified from a rat brain cDNA library\"" , "Automated change 2024-03-14: GO:0099061 replaced by GO:0098839" ;
        lego:modelstate   "production" ;
        dc:contributor    "https://orcid.org/0000-0001-5518-6584" , "https://orcid.org/0000-0001-6194-9648" ;
        dc:date           "2024-03-14" ;
        dc:title          "SYNGO_CC_2213" ;
        pav:providedBy    "https://syngo.vu.nl" ;
